ISR08769 | Mobile and IoT Computing Project | https://enr-apps.as.cmu.edu/open/SOC/SOCServlet/courseDetails?COURSE=08769&SEMESTER=S16 | instructors:Sadeh, Norman description:Students must be enrolled in 08-781 to add this project section for 3 units.
